102
00:08:38,010 --> 00:08:41,740
SR. STEVIE WONDER

103
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,450
¿Te gusta Stevie Wonder?

104
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:49,350
My Cherie Amour es
la canción de mi vida.

105
00:08:49,420 --> 00:08:50,450
Signed, Sealed, Delivered.

106
00:08:50,530 --> 00:08:52,050
No debería escribir en un violín así...

107
00:08:52,130 --> 00:08:54,560
