141
00:10:11,870 --> 00:10:13,570
Soy Steve López, del LA Times.

142
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:15,110
- López, ¿L-O-P-E-Z?
- Sí.

143
00:10:15,180 --> 00:10:17,840
