144
00:10:17,910 --> 00:10:19,140
- ¿Cómo te llamas?
- López.

145
00:10:19,210 --> 00:10:20,650
Nathaniel Anthony Ayers Junior.

146
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:23,080
N- A-T-H-A-N-l-E-L
A-N-T-H-O-N-Y

147
00:10:23,150 --> 00:10:25,080
